{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your task:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd0d  Observe the rooms through the cameras.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u26a1Fix anomalies before they get out of hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u23f3 Last the whole night: from 00:00 to 06:00.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/Floor2.gif?t=1738342511\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features of the game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc80 More than 300 unique anomalies are waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd12 13 secret endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc41\ufe0f Every change is a challenge to your attention and endurance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfda\ufe0f Deep atmosphere of fear and tension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcf9 Unique mechanics: observe, analyze, act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfaf Only the most attentive will be able to reveal all the secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/Fixed.gif?t=1738342511\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Secret Endings:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some anomalies have multiple stages and will change if not dealt with immediately. They can move between rooms. If you hear a heartbeat, it means you are in danger. Watch the cameras and see the anomaly in its entirety, but act in time to avoid danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/extras/Ending_1.gif?t=1738342511\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738342511","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic